*'''1866''': Too quick '''despairer''', wherefore wilt thou go? &mdash; Matthew Arnold, ''Thrysis A Monody''
*'''1892?''': O '''despairer''', here is my neck &mdash; Walt Whitman, ''Leaves of Grass''